name: Zero - Swirl & Demonice
body:
You can download the source code for the game, however to see the full version of the game, click on the link below

The link will bring you to a location where you will download 2 games:
1. Swirl - Recording & Execution Game.
2. Demonice - Top down game to find a balance in life.

Link to download exe file: https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BzffX1_lPaINekh1UEVVbXEybmM/view?usp=sharing
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
